name: com.N04H.techartlibrary
description:
runtime UI for games and applications.

UI Toolkit includes:

▪ A retained-mem, based on recognized web technologies, that supports stylesheets, and dynamic and contextual event handling.
▪ UXML and USS asset types for building and styling user interfaces. These are inspired by standard web technologies such as XML, HTML, and CSS.
▪ Tools and resources such as a built-in UI debugger, the support for the UI Builder visual UI authoring tool, and examples available in the editor.
